287
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] da pogleda tu Čipku koju sam izvezal.

288
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:07,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo i vidi se i na kipu

289
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,620
[SPEAKER_01] da je dodirivan.

290
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:11,200
[SPEAKER_00] Kako to nastaje.

291
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,860
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo je recimo cijela kompozicija

292
00:11:12,860 --> 00:11:14,419
[SPEAKER_00] nastala iz te mirnoće

293
00:11:14,419 --> 00:11:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] jednog vezivanja čvora

294
00:11:16,019 --> 00:11:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] i tog poteza.

295
00:11:17,139 --> 00:11:18,580
[SPEAKER_00] Nema konca između ruku.

296
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] To je skuptura.

297
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:21,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ali se taj negativan prostor

298
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,759
[SPEAKER_00] na petosti osjeća.

299
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:25,120
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se svi drugi pomaci dalje

300
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] događaju uravnoteži s tim

301
00:11:27,539 --> 00:11:29,759
[SPEAKER_00] da to bude u onom fokusu.

302
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] Tin Ujević recimo u Makarskoj

303
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:33,139
[SPEAKER_00] koji je nastao opet

304
00:11:33,139 --> 00:11:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] jesu bili jako zadovoljni

305
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,240
[SPEAKER_00] sa Svetim Petrom

306
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,320
[SPEAKER_00] pa na trgu Tina Ujevića

307
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,779
