309
00:11:40,399 --> 00:11:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je isto jedan zanimljivi trenutak.

310
00:11:42,460 --> 00:11:44,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam razmišljao o Tine

311
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:45,340
