312
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:46,679
[SPEAKER_00] meni draga ovaj pjesma

313
00:11:46,679 --> 00:11:47,720
[SPEAKER_00] Igračke vjetrova

314
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,340
