315
00:11:49,340 --> 00:11:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] upisaću tu pjesmu

316
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,840
[SPEAKER_00] na list papira, na stol

317
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] i onda sam napravio

318
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,600
[SPEAKER_00] isto jedan detalj jako zanimljiv.

319
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:58,059
[SPEAKER_00] pisao sam pjesmu

320
00:11:58,059 --> 00:11:58,740
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne do kraja.

321
00:11:58,740 --> 00:12:01,080
[SPEAKER_00] Stao sam na riječi

322
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,580
[SPEAKER_00] kad kaže

323
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:04,059
[SPEAKER_00] leti ko liće što virga vije

324
00:12:04,059 --> 00:12:05,799
[SPEAKER_00] za leti dušo

325
00:12:05,799 --> 00:12:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] ta riječ dušo

326
00:12:07,179 --> 00:12:08,879
[SPEAKER_00] koju ono treba sljedeću upisat

327
00:12:08,879 --> 00:12:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] na njoj je zastao

328
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,820
[SPEAKER_00] pomaknuo glavu

329
00:12:11,820 --> 00:12:12,500
