330
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] i eto u Makarskoj

331
00:12:13,539 --> 00:12:14,299
[SPEAKER_00] to ozrać je

332
00:12:14,299 --> 00:12:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je duša

333
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] šta

334
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] ta njegov odnos

335
00:12:16,860 --> 00:12:18,200
[SPEAKER_00] jedna se uvijek

336
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:18,620
[SPEAKER_00] našalim

337
