[SPEAKER_00] sad je tu zgodno

338
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] vidjeti ko zna

339
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] završiti ti novu pjesmu

340
