[SPEAKER_01] i onda ima dakle

345
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,799
[SPEAKER_01] nakon što ti završiš kip

346
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:29,360
[SPEAKER_01] dakle

347
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,740
[SPEAKER_01] koji proces

348
00:12:30,740 --> 00:12:31,659
[SPEAKER_01] od toga do...

349
00:12:31,659 --> 00:12:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] znači oblikovanje u glini

350
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,379
[SPEAKER_00] dominantno tog velikog kipa

351
