[SPEAKER_00] onda nastupa

352
00:12:36,019 --> 00:12:36,679
[SPEAKER_00] ljeva onica

353
00:12:36,679 --> 00:12:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] umjetnina

354
00:12:38,179 --> 00:12:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ujević recimo

355
00:12:39,159 --> 00:12:40,759
[SPEAKER_00] s kojim dugi niz godina

356
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:41,399
